export interface MemberCreateOuterInput {
  name: string;
  agent_type: string;
  prompt: string;
}
export type MemberCreateOuterOutput = string;
export type MemberCreate = (input: MemberCreateOuterInput) => MemberCreateOuterOutput;

Use this tool to create a persistent member actor in the current session.
Members are durable team/session actors and are addressed by member id or member name.
Subagent is a delegate alias, not a member alias; use RunDelegateActor when the user asks for a subagent.
